Package: nat.utils
Maintainer: Gregory Jefferis <jefferis@gmail.com>
Author: Gregory Jefferis
Version: 0.5
License: GPL-3
Title: File System Utility Functions for 'NeuroAnatomy Toolbox'
Description: Utility functions to support the 'NeuroAnatomy Toolbox' ('nat').
    Includes functions to provide a basic make style system to update files
    based on timestamp information and file locking. Convenience functions
    for working with file paths include 'abs2rel' and 'common_path'. Finally 
    there are utility functions for working with 'zip' and 'gzip' files.
Suggests:
    testthat,
    roxygen2,
    digest
